title: Ep. 213 Toni Turner: Why Tapering May Not Be Good for Stocks
itunes:title: Toni Turner: Why Tapering May Not Be Good for Stocks
description:
This week, Toni Turner, technical analysis expert and President of TrendStar Group, joins S&A Investor Radio.
 
Toni talks about trading around the upcoming Federal Reserve meeting – and also shares her favorite stock ideas.
